name: Auto & General Meeting Spaces
description: Auto & General Insurance Company Ltd offers highly competitive, quality products including car & home insurance in the Australian marketplace. A&G have kindly offered their meeting rooms on level 6 of Toowong Tower for the Brisbane Javascript meetup.
entry-instructions: Meet at the Gallery Level elevators (the same level as the train station) for pickup by security.
transport: It's a 30 second walk from the train station to the meetup. Car parking is available at Toowong Village until 10:30. Find more parking info on the Toowong Village site (https://www.toowongvillage.com.au/centre-info/getting-here/)
contactAddress: Level 6 Toowong Tower, 9 Sherwood Road, Toowong
